35:07.039 --> 35:07.840
Zhaozhao

35:10.639 --> 35:12.159
Pronto terminará

35:45.000 --> 35:45.519
Zhaozhao

35:46.320 --> 35:46.800
Zhaozhao

35:53.360 --> 35:54.599
